      "summary": "\"Something About Us\" is a song by the French electronic music duo Daft Punk. It was released as the final single from the 2001 album Discovery as a promotion for their 2003 animated feature film Interstella 5555: The 5tory of the 5ecret 5tar 5ystem. The song reached #93 on the SNEP chart ranking. <a href=\"http://www.last.fm/music/Daft+Punk/_/Something+About+Us\">Read more on Last.fm</a>.",
